{
  "stem": "23506.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He send him out, all the time, for-- for-- for catechism, to have a free hour.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he figured it like this, hey, I'm giving-- giving this kid a good time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He doesn't have to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he called my brother back and says, like this, you're sitting on the lesson and you learn everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the other kids don't know, you answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said that it was a kind of a punishment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it came handy, later on, for my brother, very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he learned catechism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because he was a good student, so the kids in his class liked him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a sense of humor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the older children, like the seven graders or the six graders, when the-- when the bell rang, they was throwing stones at him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one time a stone hit his head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had to have a couple of stitches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when my father went to the principal he said, like this, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Guterman, I love to have your son in-- in the class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because my father and my mother were members of the parents-teachers conference.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, it would be better if your son goes to the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we took him out, and he went to the Jewish public school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think that I was a fighting type at that time yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it came later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't have any Polish friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All our friends were Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know whom we know-- knew as a Pole?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- how do you say, she was taking care of the-- of the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was a-- a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
